- validate all input properly, encode and quote all output properly

- Provide a user interface for browsing the published data

- Enrich the post data on the client side

- Support for @replies

- Server-independent authentication methods

- Multiuser version

- Forward the postings to ping-the-semantic-web, Sindice, etc.

- More user interfaces than the web one: Twitter clients, SMS, Facebook, ...

